Salome Jens https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salome_Jens 0 Salome Jens (born May 8, 1935) is an American stage, film and television actress. She is perhaps best known for portraying the Female Changeling on Star Trek: Deep Space Nine in the 1990s. Salome_Jens ( born May_8_,_1935 ) is an_American_stage , film_and_television_actress .
